  "remarks": "KPi.012. Mun Cho'ng-Ch'o'l is a TCB official. In this capacity he has facilitated transactions for TCB. Tanchon was designated by the Committee in April 2009 is the main DPRK financial entity for sales of conventional arms, ballistic missiles, and goods related to the assembly and manufacture of such weapons.; Listing: First listed on 07/03/2013 (amended on 26/07/2022 and 29/06/2023)",
